{"title":"纯净的音乐","authors":["熊福林"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯净的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊福林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁耙从冬天的墙上走下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把迎春的锣鼓度节的笑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起带进田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寂静的田野便响起哗哗的水声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蛙便和父亲一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏起春的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在城市的高楼里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节晚会的余音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许还缠绕在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水泥的梁架上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但此时真正的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离我们更远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不走近田园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就永远不会知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁耙水响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这最永恒的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听着这自然和谐纯净的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方的梦正和庄稼一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在泥土的琴架上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹奏着阳光"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}